This is the bug that I wrote about when I reopened ticket SI-2431. I believe that the error is caused by the reference to the singleton object _TestData_.

Code that triggers the bug:
{code}
import org.junit.Test

class SimpleTest {
  
  @Test
  def always_fail() {
    assert(11 == TestData.value)
  }
}

object TestData {
  val value = 10
}
{code}

